Package methods.scores.bootstrap

Class Summary
Bootstrap Contains methods for the calculation of protein interaction scores using the Bootstrap approach according to Caroline C.
BootstrapMCLClustering Represents a single MCL clustering in the bootstrap scores calculation process.
BootstrapMCLClusterings Container for bootstrap MCL clustering lists.
PurificationBootstrapSamples Represents a set of bootstrap samples of a purification data set.
